<p><strong>Last updated: April 2026</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>AI-referred sessions jumped 527% in 5 months.</strong> Between January and May 2025, total AI referral sessions grew from 17,076 to 107,100 across 400+ websites studied by <a href="https://superprompt.com/blog/ai-traffic-up-527-percent-how-to-get-cited-by-chatgpt-claude-perplexity-2025">Superprompt</a>. That growth rate is not slowing down.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>AI search referral traffic is the fastest-growing traffic source on the web. Google still dominates total search volume. But ChatGPT, Perplexity, Gemini, Copilot, and Claude now send measurable visitors to websites every day. The numbers are small compared to organic search. The growth rate is not.</p>
<p>We compiled 42 AI search referral traffic statistics from Conductor, Semrush, Ahrefs, Search Engine Land, and other authoritative sources. Every stat is sourced and dated.</p>
<p>Here is what the data shows:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="#overall-ai-referral-traffic-growth">Overall AI Referral Traffic Growth (7 stats)</a></li>
<li><a href="#platform-market-share">Platform Market Share (7 stats)</a></li>
<li><a href="#conversion-rates-and-traffic-quality">Conversion Rates and Traffic Quality (7 stats)</a></li>
<li><a href="#ai-overviews-and-zero-click-impact">AI Overviews and Zero-Click Impact (7 stats)</a></li>
<li><a href="#industry-specific-ai-traffic">Industry-Specific AI Traffic (7 stats)</a></li>
<li><a href="#growth-projections-and-predictions">Growth Projections and Predictions (7 stats)</a></li>
<li><a href="#key-takeaways">Key Takeaways</a></li>
</ul>
<p><img loading="lazy" alt="AI search referral traffic statistics 2026 showing 527% growth and platform breakdown" src="/images/blog/ai-search-referral-traffic-overview.webp" /></p>
<h2>Overall AI Referral Traffic Growth</h2>
<p><strong>1. AI-referred sessions grew 527% in 5 months (January to May 2025).</strong> Sessions jumped from 17,076 to 107,100 across 400+ websites and 12 industries. (Source: <a href="https://superprompt.com/blog/ai-traffic-up-527-percent-how-to-get-cited-by-chatgpt-claude-perplexity-2025">Superprompt / Previsible AI Traffic Report</a>, 2025)</p>
<p><strong>2. AI platforms generated 1.13 billion referral visits in June 2025.</strong> That represents a 357% increase from June 2024. (Source: <a href="https://digiday.com/media/in-graphic-detail-the-state-of-ai-referral-traffic-in-2025/">Digiday</a>, 2025)</p>
<p><strong>3. AI referral traffic now accounts for 1.08% of all website traffic.</strong> It grows approximately 1 percentage point month over month. (Source: <a href="https://www.asklantern.com/blogs/chatgpt-drives-87-of-ai-referral-traffic">Conductor</a>, 2026)</p>
<p><strong>4. AI referral traffic grew 700% in 2025.</strong> Full-year growth outpaced most other traffic sources by orders of magnitude. (Source: <a href="https://searchengineland.com/ai-traffic-up-seo-rewritten-459954">Search Engine Land</a>, 2025)</p>
<p><strong>5. Gen AI traffic is growing 165x faster than organic search traffic.</strong> Organic still dominates in volume. AI dominates in growth velocity. (Source: <a href="https://www.superlines.io/articles/ai-search-statistics/">Superlines</a>, 2026)</p>
<p><strong>6. Traffic to the top 10 AI chatbots grew 81% year over year in 2025.</strong> Total visits reached 55.2 billion. (Source: <a href="https://www.position.digital/blog/ai-seo-statistics/">Similarweb via Position Digital</a>, 2025)</p>
<p><strong>7. AI search tools captured 12% to 15% of global search market share by end of 2025.</strong> Up from 5% to 6% at the start of the year. (Source: <a href="https://almcorp.com/blog/ai-search-trends/">ALM Corp</a>, 2025)</p>
<p>For more context on how these shifts affect your SEO strategy, see our guide on <a href="/blog/ai-search-changing-seo/">how AI search is changing SEO</a>.</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" alt="AI referral traffic platform market share breakdown showing ChatGPT, Perplexity, Copilot, and Gemini" src="/images/blog/ai-referral-platform-share.webp" /></p>
<h2>Platform Market Share</h2>
<p><strong>8. ChatGPT drives 87.4% of all AI referral traffic.</strong> No other platform comes close. (Source: <a href="https://www.asklantern.com/blogs/chatgpt-drives-87-of-ai-referral-traffic">Conductor</a>, 2026)</p>
<p><strong>9. ChatGPT referral traffic grew 200%+ year over year from Q1 2025 to Q1 2026.</strong> (Source: <a href="https://www.siegemedia.com/strategy/chatgpt-referral-traffic-data">Siege Media</a>, 2026)</p>
<p><strong>10. Perplexity accounts for 15% of all AI referral traffic.</strong> It reaches nearly 20% in the United States. (Source: <a href="https://seranking.com/blog/ai-traffic-research-study/">SE Ranking</a>, 2025)</p>
<p><strong>11. Google Gemini referral traffic grew 388% between September and November 2025.</strong> That growth rate outpaced ChatGPT in the same period. (Source: <a href="https://digiday.com/media/in-graphic-detail-the-state-of-ai-referral-traffic-in-2025/">Digiday</a>, 2025)</p>
<p><strong>12. Microsoft Copilot referral traffic grew 25.2x in 2025.</strong> Copilot uses Bing's search index for grounding. Strong Bing SEO directly influences Copilot visibility. (Source: <a href="https://superprompt.com/blog/ai-traffic-up-527-percent-how-to-get-cited-by-chatgpt-claude-perplexity-2025">Superprompt</a>, 2025)</p>
<p><strong>13. Claude grew 12.8x in referral traffic in 2025.</strong> Despite having the smallest referral volume among major platforms, Claude sends the highest-value visitors. (Source: <a href="https://superprompt.com/blog/ai-traffic-up-527-percent-how-to-get-cited-by-chatgpt-claude-perplexity-2025">Superprompt</a>, 2025)</p>
<p><strong>14. Google AI Overviews now reach 1.5 billion monthly users.</strong> That makes it the largest AI search surface by audience size. (Source: <a href="https://www.superlines.io/articles/ai-search-statistics/">Superlines</a>, 2026)</p>
<p>To get your site cited by these platforms, read our guide on <a href="/blog/get-cited-ai-search/">how to get cited in AI search</a>.</p>
