<p><strong>38. The GEO market is valued at $848 million in 2025.</strong> It is projected to reach $33.7 billion by 2034 at a 50.5% CAGR. (Source: <a href="https://www.superlines.io/articles/ai-search-statistics/">Dimension Market Research via Superlines</a>, 2025)</p>
