<h2>FAQ</h2>
<p><strong>How much has AI search referral traffic grown?</strong></p>
<p>AI referral sessions grew 527% between January and May 2025. Full-year 2025 growth reached 700%. AI platforms generated 1.13 billion referral visits in June 2025 alone, a 357% increase from June 2024.</p>
<p><strong>Which AI platform sends the most referral traffic?</strong></p>
<p>ChatGPT drives 87.4% of all AI referral traffic. Perplexity is second at 15%. Google Gemini is the fastest growing at 388% growth in late 2025. Microsoft Copilot grew 25.2x in the same period.</p>
<p><strong>Does AI referral traffic convert better than organic search?</strong></p>
<p>Yes. Multiple studies show AI traffic converts at 4.4x to 23x the rate of organic search. ChatGPT ecommerce traffic converts 31% higher than non-branded organic. AI-referred visitors spend 68% more time on sites.</p>
<p><strong>How do Google AI Overviews affect organic traffic?</strong></p>
<p>AI Overviews appear on 48% of Google searches as of March 2026. They reduce organic CTR by 61%. But brands cited in AI Overviews earn 35% more organic clicks than uncited brands. Getting cited is now critical.</p>
<p><strong>What industries get the most AI referral traffic?</strong></p>
<p>IT leads at 2.8% of total traffic from AI. Legal (1.34%), finance (1.21%), and healthcare (0.89%) follow. Legal saw the fastest growth at 823% year over year. Consumer electronics, travel, and financial services show 40% to 55% AI-influenced purchase rates.</p>
<p><strong>How can I optimize my website for AI search referral traffic?</strong></p>
<p>Start with strong traditional SEO. It accounts for 77% of AI visibility. Then add structured data, clear answer formatting, and an <a href="/blog/llms-txt-guide/">llms.txt file</a>. Do not block AI crawlers. For a full strategy, see our <a href="/blog/generative-engine-optimization-guide/">GEO guide</a>.</p>
